1
00:00:07,680 --> 00:00:08,960
(DOG BARKING)

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:13,480
I still can't believe I'm allowed him.

3
00:00:15,040 --> 00:00:16,880
-He's your son.
-That's what I'm talking about.

4
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:19,160
I mean, who authorised this?

5
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:22,520
It's the single most terrifying thing
that's ever happened to me.

6
00:00:23,160 --> 00:00:26,200
-I mean, what if I break him?
-Yeah, you best try not to do that.

7
00:00:26,760 --> 00:00:27,960
(BABY GURGLING)

8
00:00:32,040 --> 00:00:33,400
You all right, mate?

9
00:00:34,280 --> 00:00:35,800
See? Nothing!

10
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:37,440
(ELECTRICAL BUZZING)

11
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:40,160
He's fine. He loves you.

12
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:42,560
See?

13
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:44,920
-(BABY GURGLING)
-Hey!

14
00:00:48,680 --> 00:00:51,120
It's just when I look into his eyes,
I see everything I'm going to do wrong

15
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:53,320
for the next 60 years
reflected back at me.

16
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:56,120
You're going to be an amazing dad,
"cause you're an amazing man.

17
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:02,280
Okay.

18
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:04,120
(BABY GURGLING)

19
00:01:04,840 --> 00:01:06,640
Huh? That's good.

20
00:01:09,520 --> 00:01:11,160
Still not broken.

21
00:01:13,480 --> 00:01:15,440
Another one. Have you seen
all these people disappearing?

22
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:17,160
And you're absolutely sure about this?

23
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:19,280
Me and him on our own
for a whole weekend?

24
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:21,080
Of course,
what is the worst that could happen?

25
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:23,760
Don't ever say that! If you say that,
terrible things will happen.

26
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,200
Have you never seen a film?

27
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:26,880
Come on, it's his bath time.

28
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:29,640
What? We literally
just did that yesterday.

29
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:35,000
Oh, for God's sake, stop your fussing.
Everything is going to be fine.

30
00:01:35,760 --> 00:01:38,480
It's wet elbows,
not the end of the world. Come on.

31
00:01:39,440 --> 00:01:41,800
Fine. Let's get you in the bath.

32
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:44,720
Do I have to bath him while you're gone?

33
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:48,080
(GLASS SHATTERING)

